  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Combine Slovenia and Austria on an exciting multi-centre holiday to the popular destinations of Lake Bled and Kitzbühel</h2>
<p>Start your holiday with a stay in <a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled</a>, famous for the small, church-topped Bled Island which is reached by historic Pletna boat. Take a walk up to Bled Castle for the best views over the lake, or head to the Straža Hill to ride the exhilarating summer roller-coaster. There's plenty to explore on foot in Bled, from leisurely loops of the lake to exploring the surrounding forested hills and pretty villages. The second half of your holiday is in <a data-udi="umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739}" title="Kitzbuhel">Kitzbühel</a>, a small-but-vibrant city in Austria, home to one of the largest walking trail networks in Austria and stunning mountain views. There's around 1,000 kilometres of hiking trails to choose from, plus a range of activities to try.</p>
<h3>Guide price from: £1,810pp*</h3>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options: </h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Combine stays of 3, 4, 7, 10 or 11 nights into a total holiday duration of 7, 10, 11 or 14 nights</li>
<li>Travel and change destinations on a Wednesday or Saturday</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from UK</li>
<li>Transfers from the airport to your hotel in Bled, between destinations (via Salzburg airport) and from your hotel in Kitzbühel to the airport</li>
<li>Accommodation in your chosen hotel in each destination</li>
</ul>
</ul>
