  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Spend a few days exploring the famously-photogenic Lake Bled in Slovenia - take a Pletna Boat to the iconic Bled Island and immerse yourself into Slovenian culture. Then take a transfer via Salzburg Airport to Kitzbühel, one of Austria's most-loved hiking destinations and discover the colourful, cobbled centre and miles of scenic walking trails.</p>]]></listingDescription>
