  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>A multi-centre holiday lets you combine multiple destinations and exciting activities to create your ideal trip. Enjoy everything from panoramic walks, cultural tours and outdoor adventures to relaxing days and tasty local cuisine.</p>
<h3>Visit Slovenia's famously-photogenic Lake Bled </h3>
<p>Lake Bled is a must-see part of Slovenia, famous for Bled Island and the impressive Bled Castle which offers some of the best views of the lake from above. Take a stroll round the lake, stopping for a refreshing swim at the western-most point, or tread the walkways through the Vintgar Gorge. Water-lovers can do much more than just swim - hire a paddleboard or kayak for a few hours, or take a historic Pletna Boat to the island. Make sure to take a day trip to <a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj">Lake Bohinj</a> for a trip up Mount Vogel or a walk along the Mostnica Gorge.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More About Lake Bled</a></p>
<h3>Visit the vibrant city of Kitzbühel and discover lots of scenic walking trails</h3>
<p>With a walking trail network of around 1,000 kilometres, Kitzbühel's is one of the largest in Austria and it offers something for everyone, with incredible views at every turn. In the colourful centre, you'll find restaurants and cafes serving up everything from traditional, hearty food to fine dining, and designer boutiques line the cobbled streets. There's a variety of lifts that open up the walking area, and take you to some of the best viewpoints with ease too, and for the adventure-seekers there's a multitude of activities to try.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0424394c50b54ef4848722ee185d0739}" title="Kitzbuhel" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More About Kitzbühel</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><em>Please note: This is an independent multi-centre holiday and you are free to choose your own itinerary in each destination. The above contains recommendations which are provided for information only and are not included in the price of your holiday. An Inghams Destination Expert will be on hand locally either in resort or by telephone and will provide advice and offer optional excursions and walking passes.</em></p>
<p><em>Special diets, including vegetarian, must be requested prior to booking.</em></p>
<p><em>The itineraries may be subject to change. Where this becomes necessary, and where practicable, we will take the steps as outlined in clause 5 of our <a data-udi="umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">terms and conditions</a>.</em></p>]]></locationDescription>
